#Sample Feature Definition Template
@tag
Feature: User Creation

  @tag1
  Scenario: To verify admin user creation on orange HRM application
    Given User login the application
    And Enter username and password
    And click on login button
    When User click on admin module
    Then User navigate to admin list page
    When User click on add button
    And Enter all the mandatory details
    And User click on save button
    Then admin user created successfully

  #@tag2
  #Scenario Outline: Title of your scenario outline
    #Given I want to write a step with <name>
    #When I check for the <value> in step
    #Then I verify the <status> in step
